  user_input {
    user_response: "Create a website for ALAN, my custom Ableton Live AI assistant plugin that can make edits within Ableton Live based on text-chat prompts. The website should feel futuristic and next-era, with a dark theme, glowing accents, and smooth interactive animations. It should showcase ALAN\'s capabilities and how ALAN looks and functions within the DAW. For now, these can be images of any plugin in Ableton Live. The website should be simple. The homepage should be ALAN, the second page should be Docs, the third page should be About, and the final page should be Support. The homepage should fill the screen, and elements should change interactively as a user scrolls down through the pages. "
    items {
      text: "Create a website for ALAN, my custom Ableton Live AI assistant plugin that can make edits within Ableton Live based on text-chat prompts. The website should feel futuristic and next-era, with a dark theme, glowing accents, and smooth interactive animations. It should showcase ALAN\'s capabilities and how ALAN looks and functions within the DAW. For now, these can be images of any plugin in Ableton Live. The website should be simple. The homepage should be ALAN, the second page should be Docs, the third page should be About, and the final page should be Support. The homepage should fill the screen, and elements should change interactively as a user scrolls down through the pages. "
