  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Designing ALAN\'s Website**\n\nI\'m focusing on the website for ALAN, specifically on giving it a futuristic feel. I\'m exploring dark themes with glowing accents and interactive animations, to create a next-era vibe. I\'m thinking about how to best showcase ALAN\'s capabilities in a visually engaging way.\n\n\n**Defining Website Structure**\n\nI\'ve got the website\'s structure more clearly defined. I\'ve broken it down into four key sections: ALAN (homepage), Docs, About, and Support. I\'m prioritizing a simple design, but one that is visually engaging. I\'m planning the homepage as a full-screen, interactive experience that changes as a user scrolls. I\'m focusing on showcasing ALAN\'s abilities and functions within a DAW.\n\n\n**Visualizing User Interactions**\n\nI\'m now picturing a highly interactive homepage element where users can generate a tech house bassline, quantize MIDI, and map macros, seeing dynamic mockups of Ableton UI elements responding. This would be very engaging and perfectly align with showcasing ALAN within a DAW. Image generation is relevant, for producing visuals of the ALAN plugin in Ableton.\n\n\n"
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 3
      nanos: 707617358
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
