  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Designing SupportSection**\n\nI\'ve successfully designed the `SupportSection` component (`src/components/SupportSection.tsx`). It\'s exciting to have all the standard components in place: `Navigation.tsx`, `DAWSimulator.tsx`, `DocsSection.tsx`, and `AboutSection.tsx`. Now, let\'s move forward!\n\n\n**Envisioning Support Interface**\n\nI am now envisioning a novel support page, blending a glassmorphic contact form with a terminal-like interface. The plan involves a left-side form with standard fields, and on the right side, a \"Support Terminal Live Logger.\" This logger would provide a visual, animated feedback loop for users submitting support tickets, adding to the aesthetic. The terminal output would mimic system messages, and once a ticket is submitted, it would trigger a custom congratulations overlay.\n\n\n"
