  user_input {
    user_response: "Apply the \"Clean Minimalism\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Clean Minimalism\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML: <!doctype html>\\n<html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n  <head>\\n    <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n    <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n    <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n    <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n    <style>\\n      body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n      /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n      .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n      .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n      .flex { display: flex; }\\n      .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n      .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n    </style>\\n  </head>\\n  <body>\\n    <div class=\\\"w-[1024px] h-[768px] bg-[#050505] text-slate-100 flex flex-col font-sans overflow-hidden selection:bg-cyan-500/30\\\"><div class=\\\"absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full h-full pointer-events-none opacity-40\\\"><div class=\\\"absolute top-[-10%] left-[-10%] w-[50%] h-[50%] bg-cyan-500/10 rounded-full blur-[120px]\\\"></div><div class=\\\"absolute bottom-[-10%] right-[-10%] w-[40%] h-[40%] bg-purple-600/10 rounded-full blur-[120px]\\\"></div></div><nav class=\\\"relative z-10 flex items-center justify-between px-12 h-24 border-b border-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm bg-black/20\\\"><div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2\\\"><div class=\\\"w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-tr from-cyan-400 to-purple-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\\\"><span class=\\\"text-black font-black text-xs\\\">A</span></div><span class=\\\"text-xl font-bold tracking-tighter\\\">ALAN<span class=\\\"text-cyan-400\\\">.</span></span></div><div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-10 text-sm font-medium text-slate-400\\\"><a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"text-cyan-400\\\">Homepage</a><a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"hover:text-white transition-colors\\\">Docs</a><a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"hover:text-white transition-colors\\\">About</a><a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"hover:text-white transition-colors\\\">Support</a></div><button class=\\\"px-6 py-2 bg-white text-black text-xs font-bold rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-cyan-400 transition-all\\\">Download Alpha</button></nav><main class=\\\"relative z-10 flex-1 grid grid-cols-2 items-center px-12 gap-12\\\"><div class=\\\"space-y-8\\\"><div class=\\\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 bg-cyan-500/10 border border-cyan-500/20 rounded-full text-cyan-400 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest\\\">Next-Era Plugin Technology</div><h1 class=\\\"text-7xl font-bold leading-[0.9] tracking-tighter\\\">Your DAW,<br/>but with a <span class=\\\"text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-purple-400\\\">brain.</span></h1><p class=\\\"text-lg text-slate-400 max-w-md leading-relaxed\\\">The first generative AI assistant living inside Ableton Live. Compose, mix, and automate your workflow with natural language prompts.</p><div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-6\\\"><div class=\\\"flex flex-col\\\"><span class=\\\"text-2xl font-mono font-bold text-white\\\">0.4ms</span><span class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase text-slate-500 tracking-widest\\\">Latency</span></div><div class=\\\"w-px h-8 bg-white/10\\\"></div><div class=\\\"flex flex-col\\\"><span class=\\\"text-2xl font-mono font-bold text-white\\\">GPT-4o</span><span class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase text-slate-500 tracking-widest\\\">Engine</span></div><div class=\\\"w-px h-8 bg-white/10\\\"></div><div class=\\\"flex flex-col\\\"><span class=\\\"text-2xl font-mono font-bold text-white\\\">Native</span><span class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase text-slate-500 tracking-widest\\\">Integration</span></div></div></div><div class=\\\"relative group\\\"><div class=\\\"absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500 to-purple-600 rounded-2xl blur opacity-25 group-hover:opacity-40 transition duration-1000 group-hover:duration-200\\\"></div><div class=\\\"relative bg-[#0F0F0F] border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-2xl\\\"><div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between mb-8 border-b border-white/5 pb-4\\\"><div class=\\\"flex gap-1.5\\\"><div class=\\\"w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-red-500/50\\\"></div><div class=\\\"w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-amber-500/50\\\"></div><div class=\\\"w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/50\\\"></div></div><div class=\\\"text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-500\\\">ALAN_V1.0.AMXD</div><div class=\\\"w-4 h-4 rounded border border-white/20\\\"></div></div><div class=\\\"space-y-6\\\"><div class=\\\"bg-black/40 rounded-lg p-4 border border-white/5\\\"><div class=\\\"text-[10px] text-cyan-400 uppercase tracking-tighter mb-2\\\">User Prompt</div><div class=\\\"text-sm italic text-slate-300\\\">\\\"Slice the vocal loop on track 3 every 8th note and add a rhythmic delay that follows the tempo...\\\"</div></div><div class=\\\"flex flex-col gap-3\\\"><div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2\\\"><div class=\\\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-cyan-400 animate-pulse shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(34,211,238,0.8)]\\\"></div><span class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold text-slate-400\\\">Processing Sequence</span></div><div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-12 gap-1\\\"><div class=\\\"h-8 bg-cyan-500/40 rounded-sm border border-cyan-500/50\\\"></div